show.description:
Srishti, the daughter of a wealthy industrialist, who is presumed dead after a tragic accident. However, years later, she returns under a new identity, completely transformed — both in appearance and attitude.
Unrecognizable and emotionally hardened, Srishti is now on a mission to reclaim her rightful place and uncover the dark truths behind her family's betrayal. The people closest to her — including family members and former lovers — are caught off-guard as she begins to dismantle the corrupt empire that rose in her absence.
The show navigates themes of revenge, identity, inheritance, and justice, layered with emotional confrontations and shocking reveals. With each episode, Srishti inches closer to exposing those who wronged her and regaining control of her legacy — but not without personal sacrifices.
